title: Swami's Cafe
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Lacto, Ovo, American, Fast food, Juice bar, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Casual cafe with a few locations. Offers a varied menu including some vegetarian options and a few vegan choices. Breakfast all day, salads, sandwiches and wraps, juices and smoothies, and more. Prices cheap for the veggie items. Small interior with counter and stool in addition to a large patio with a fountain.
